Rules.InvariantScript: "Search by Name, Email, Task ID, Title"
If (TrackRequestComponent.IsAdmin, Parent.Width - Self.X - Header_TaskID_TRC.Width - Header_Title_TRC.Width - Header_Comments_TRC.Width - Header_State_TRC.Width, 0 )

If( !IsError(ThisItem.DisplayName) && !IsError(ThisItem.UserPrincipalEmail), If(ThisItem.IsSelected, "", "") & ThisItem.DisplayName & "
E: " & ThisItem.UserPrincipalEmail & If(ThisItem.IsSelected, "", ""), "" & ThisItem.UserPrincipalEmail & " is not valid.", "(No Value)" )

If(App.Width < 800, 
    If(TrackRequestComponent.IsAdmin, App.Width * 0.6, App.Width * 0.43),
    If(TrackRequestComponent.IsAdmin, App.Width * 0.5, App.Width * 0.32)
)
